<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٩ص١٦٠:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{وَأُوحِيَ إِلَيَّ هَذَا الْقُرْآنُ لِأُنْذِرَكُمْ بِهِ وَمَنْ بَلَغَ}</span> <span class="c4">[الأنعام: ١٩]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{لِأُنْذِرَكُمْ بِهِ}</span>: <span class="c2">«يَعْنِي أَهْلَ مَكَّةَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{وَمَنْ بَلَغَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«هَذَا القُرْآنُ , فَهُوَ لَهُ نَذِيرٌ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>